{"_path":"/maps/_ai/safety","_dir":"_ai","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"安全 (Safety)","description":"","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h1","props":{"id":"安全-safety"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"安全 (Safety)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"constitutional-ai价值观对齐的宪法方法"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Constitutional AI：价值观对齐的宪法方法"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Constitutional AI 由 Anthropic 提出，核心思想是让模型遵循一组\"宪法原则\"进行自我修正。不同于 RLHF 需要大量人工标注，它通过 AI 自我批评和修订实现价值观对齐——模型生成回答后根据宪法原则自我批评并改进，再用改进后的回答训练偏好模型。这种方法减少了对人工反馈的依赖，更易扩展到多语言、多文化场景。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2212.08073","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Constitutional AI 论文"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.anthropic.com/constitution","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Claude's Constitution"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://blog.bluedot.org/p/what-is-constitutional-ai","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"BlueDot 解读"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"llamaguard输入输出内容审核模型"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LlamaGuard：输入输出内容审核模型"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LlamaGuard 是 Meta 开源的输入/输出内容审核模型，基于 Llama 架构微调，可对对话内容进行安全风险分类。覆盖暴力与犯罪、仇恨言论、自残、性相关内容、恶意软件、欺诈/诈骗、隐私侵犯等 7 大类风险。最新 Llama Guard 3 支持多模态（图像理解）内容审核，是构建安全 AI 系统的关键组件。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2312.06674","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LlamaGuard 论文"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://ai.meta.com/research/publications/llama-guard-llm-based-input-output-safeguard-for-human-ai-conversations/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Meta AI 发布"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://ai.meta.com/research/publications/llama-guard-3-vision-safeguarding-human-ai-image-understanding-conversations/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Llama Guard 3 Vision"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"nemo-guardrails三层防护对话安全框架"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"NeMo Guardrails：三层防护对话安全框架"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"NeMo Guardrails 是 NVIDIA 推出的对话安全框架，提供输入防护（检测并拦截恶意提示）、对话管理（控制对话流程防止话题偏离）、输出防护（审核模型回复过滤不安全内容）三层防护。与 LlamaGuard、Cleanlab TLM 集成，支持 LangChain、LlamaIndex 等主流框架，是可编程的 LLM 安全工具包。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://docs.nvidia.com/nemo/guardrails/latest/index.html","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"NeMo Guardrails 文档"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://developer.nvidia.com/blog/content-moderation-and-safety-checks-with-nvidia-nemo-guardrails/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"NVIDIA 博客"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/NVIDIA-NeMo/Guardrails","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"GitHub"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"prompt-guard提示注入与越狱检测"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Prompt Guard：提示注入与越狱检测"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Prompt Guard 是 Meta 专门用于检测提示注入（Prompt Injection）和越狱（Jailbreak）攻击的模型。Prompt Guard 2 有两个版本：86M（支持多语言攻击检测）和 22M（超轻量版适合边缘部署）。两者都经过大量已知漏洞语料训练，可检测直接注入（用户试图覆盖系统提示）、间接注入（通过外部数据源注入恶意指令）和越狱攻击。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://huggingface.co/meta-llama/Llama-Prompt-Guard-2-86M","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Prompt Guard 86M"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://huggingface.co/meta-llama/Llama-Prompt-Guard-2-22M","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Prompt Guard 22M"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://ai.meta.com/blog/ai-defenders-program-llama-protection-tools/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Meta 发布说明"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"多层防御安全不能依赖单点"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"多层防御：安全不能依赖单点"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"有效的 LLM 安全需要多层防御架构：输入层使用 Prompt Guard 检测注入攻击，内容层使用 LlamaGuard 进行风险分类，输出层再次审核过滤不安全内容。永远不要依赖单一防线，攻击者总能找到绕过单个防护的方法。定期红队测试、记录分析被拒绝的请求、建立人工审核机制处理边界案例，是持续保持安全性的关键。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.datocms-assets.com/75231/1752004377-llm-security-best-practices-v2.pdf","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LLM 安全最佳实践"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.datadoghq.com/blog/llm-guardrails-best-practices/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Datadog Guardrails 指南"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.sentinelone.com/cybersecurity-101/cybersecurity/defense-in-depth-ai-cybersecurity/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Defense in Depth 指南"}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"constitutional-ai价值观对齐的宪法方法","depth":2,"text":"Constitutional AI：价值观对齐的宪法方法"},{"id":"llamaguard输入输出内容审核模型","depth":2,"text":"LlamaGuard：输入输出内容审核模型"},{"id":"nemo-guardrails三层防护对话安全框架","depth":2,"text":"NeMo Guardrails：三层防护对话安全框架"},{"id":"prompt-guard提示注入与越狱检测","depth":2,"text":"Prompt Guard：提示注入与越狱检测"},{"id":"多层防御安全不能依赖单点","depth":2,"text":"多层防御：安全不能依赖单点"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_ai:safety.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_ai/safety.md","_stem":"6.maps/_ai/safety","_extension":"md"}